article_title: New State Data On Obamacare Enrollment Trends Show How Scheme Is Failing

article_metadata.description: The White House obfuscates when it comes to Obamacare enrollment results. But some of the individual states that have established their own on-line exchanges (and sidestepped healthcare.gov) have been forthcoming. Enrollment in these states is outpacing healthcare.gov. So it's a good bet that their experience is a proxy of what’s happening market [...]
article_metadata.author: Scott Gottlieb
